Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:51.19,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What Lies on the Opposite Shore
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After the third day of the new year,\Nmy health was restored.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:01:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A few days passed since I came back home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It feels strange.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until the day before yesterday,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it was... it was so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was so lively...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Has the air conditioner always been this loud?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Has the clock always been so noisy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh no...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Walk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is bad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know this feeling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I can't meet eyes with it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Walk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know it, but I mustn't think that name.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I say that name,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be dealt a blow that tears up my insides.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't think.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Walk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}2-e-Pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}8-h-Bishop+.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Same-Silver General.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}2-b-Silver General.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}4-h-Silver General.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}3-c-Silver General.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}7-g-Silver General.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I stand still,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't be able to move again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot. We're out of milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it. Why didn't I buy more?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:05:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do? I bet it's freezing outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can go buy some.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Your cold would come roaring back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The kotatsu is scary, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once you sit under it, you can't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}When you're under it, it really warms you up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}but it's three times as cold when you get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know it,\Nbut you can't stay away from it, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right? After all, it's so warm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it makes you happy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. Their house is like a kotatsu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I'm inside, it's so warm\Nand comfortable, I almost melt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But when I leave, I realize the daily life\NI was fine with before{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is actually freezing cold,\Nand I'm painfully reminded of that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I think deeply about it, I get so scared\Nthat my whole body gets the chills.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know, but I have to think.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Calm down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.\NFirst, sort out the current situation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, if I stop thinking\Nand stand still, I'll be stalemated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have three more\Nrank-deciding matches this season.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the moment, I have\Nfour wins and three losses.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't rise in rank this season,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I need to get back on track,\Nand connect that with next year.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then, the title matches.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only thing I'm continuously\Nwinning through is coming next week.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Lion King Tournament:\Nthe qualifier tournament.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For now, I need to focus on that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the number of my victories decrease,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll eventually lose my place, just like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the one thing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that I won't let happen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shogi Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Lion King Tournament.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}19th Lion King\NTournament
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the shogi tournament sponsored by\Nthe biggest newspaper in Japan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This and the Master Tournament\Nare the two major title-tournaments.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The tournament has six groups of players,\Nsplit according{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to their records from the previous year.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The top-ranking players of each class\Ncan participate in the main tournament.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Because it has such huge sponsors, the scale\Nis much bigger than other shogi tournaments{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}and it gets a lot of media attention.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}So of course, this raises\Nthe spirits of the players, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But what gets the shogi players\Neven more excited is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One win nets you 600 thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:01.52,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Glass Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}Grab
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two wins gets you 1.2 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the generous prize money.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Lion King Tournament sure fires you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:10.70,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tap\NTap
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:10.70,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeeze
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}In golf, it would be the Japan Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}In tennis, it would be the U.S. Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's get some, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot. It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Status, glory, money. All of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My opponent is Takeshi Tsujii, 9th dan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"three clauses" and "Santa Claus"\Nsound similar, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Icy... roses are beautiful, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just... kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:56.07,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Super\NCold
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's a shogi player\Nwith strong offensive power...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...in more ways than one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the most amazing thing is that even while\Ncracking lame jokes, he plays a strong game.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}H-He's strong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As expected from a 9th dan,\NRank A for eight years!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To kill a man on Kilimanjaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See what I did there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really don't want to lose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't wanna lose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this feeling!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}He's bringing out the bishop?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:44.37,DefaultLow2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Smith's Opponent\NOkuyasu Yokomizo, 7th dan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}What is this? A trap?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It may or may not be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's nagging at me, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}above anything else...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}if I use my Bishop to take his Silver,\Nhis Gold will take my Bishop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That knight could be mine too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dangle-dangle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And in the enemy camp!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Rook
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can promote my rook!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to take his knight here, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:14.69,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bishop
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:14.69,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silver General         Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I sacrifice my Bishop,\NI'll get his Knight and Silver in exchange.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Plus my Rook will become a dragon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's like my mentor said.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Women may betray you,\Nbut stolen pieces never will."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right. Well, that's what would happen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Silver  Dragon  Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Satisfied
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So for now, I'll pull my dragon back...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Poison chestnut!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Pawn
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Stabbed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Don't\Ntake it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Take it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I take the 2-g-Pawn,\Nmy Dragon would do it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His turn, 4-i-Bishop{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My turn, 2-h-Dragon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His turn, 6-g-Pawn+{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:06.62,OnTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take it\NDon't take it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't take it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my turn, 3-h-Dragon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His move, 2-h-Bishop, and that's bad for me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No wait... is this already over?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The castle's on fire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And something's stabbing me in the back?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I... I lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a9}Mr. Yokomizo\NYou died at 2h,\Nwhile holding\NKnight and Silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Smith's Mysterious Dungeon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From where? From the Bishop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or before that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you guys in the middle\Nof your own match?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now, go on.\NConcentrate on your own board.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:12:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was also at the end of an intense,\Nquagmire-filled rendezvous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kiriyama 5th-Dan\NTsujii 9th-Dan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I narrowly got a win on the 187th move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama 5th-Dan, wins on the 187th move
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I drew... my own draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could say that,\Nbut today, you sealed the deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sealed... sealed the ceiling seal deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please. That's enough. No more...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at my limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:37.50,DefaultLef2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too\Nmuch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...in more ways than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:40.55,SMR,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Special Match Room                  Takao\NLion King Tournament     Lion King Tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:40.55,LeftSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Masamune Gotou\NKenichirou Irie
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:40.55,CenterSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei Kiriyama\NTakeshi Tsujii
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:40.55,RightSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuyuki Misumi\NOkuyasu Yokomizo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got Gotou next? Wish I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, that old dude is pretty scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what it is,\Nbut he's got a yakuza aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just sitting in front of him\Nmakes you make mistakes. Yikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap! Speak of the devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:20.01,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What Lies on the Opposite Shore
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:23.01,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black River (Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep going like this,\Nyou and I will go head to head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm looking forward to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It should be a little more interesting\Nthan beating you with my bare hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to pass on a message\Nto your old man, Kouda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's about that stalker girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him to get her off my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotou gave it to me recently.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love him. I truly love him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's really annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on there, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As for you, Mr. Gotou, if there's something\Nyou want to say, please tell Mr. Kouda directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please! New people like him are vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Is somebody still on the 4th floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The fortune fishing boat's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Chairman!\NPlease don't take your fish out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, at a time like this,\Nanother troublemaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, Kiriyama. Calm down, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The noisy guy's back, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going. Remember to tell Kouda, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Scary. He's like, what, a heavyweight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy and tenacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If he's crude oil, I'm salad oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice and light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen\Nbetween you and Gotou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}He was saying some ominous things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the tackle master is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Slippery{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? I'm not seeing any smiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Japan Shogi Association
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? 62 centimeters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about some sashimi and hot sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman, shhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Some people are still in their match! Shhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no. Whoops, sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Slap
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Avalanche
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take whatever you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nakamura!\NBring some bags you can put fish in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, tell everyone from Modern Shogi\Ndownstairs to come up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unlimited capturing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about this, Smith? 40 sardines!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Stuffed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't. A bachelor probably\Ncan't handle 40 fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal with the teardrop sunglasses?\NI thought it was some old hipster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind the fish. Please introduce me\Nto a woman who will fillet fish, Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Blunt
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Crammed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Gotou should've taken some home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since he's a married man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His wife's still in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamura! Are these all the bags we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'll look for more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll take these bluish ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that called again? DHA?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.07,0:17:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was popular, supposed to be\Ngood for the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, have a good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat this and come up\Nwith countermeasures against Gotou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'd better head out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.21,0:17:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Wham
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from the owner at Bar Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Crunch\NCrunch
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you've been enjoying the hospitality\Nof her beautiful niece at that house lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Owowow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should keep that a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of our association's members\Nwho are head-over-heels for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Heavy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Heavy! Reek{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gross. Do you smell something fishy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If she's taking care of you,\Nwhy don't you bring her some?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The owner proudly said she's a good cook.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He loaded me down with fish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Filleting them will probably be a real chore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What if this just becomes a burden to her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I'm inside, it's so warm\Nand comfortable,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I almost melt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This house is like a kotatsu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm scared that I'll never\Nbe able to leave again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I thought to stay away for a while.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But here I am.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Fwap{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Quiver Quiver
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fillet the rockfish into three, fry them up,\Nand have them for tomorrow's lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll slice the sardines into anchovies\Nand save them for pizza and pasta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fillet the flounder into five pieces,\Nsplit it into salted fish and sashimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How many days of food expenses\Nwill we save from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is wonderful! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Dash{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We got extravagant for New Year's,\Nso she told us to be frugal for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now we can have delicious food\Nfrom tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- Standby.\N- Okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Streamlined{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miso soup with cabbage and deep-fried tofu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kinpira-style lotus root and carrots.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Warm rice with raw egg.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We were already done eating.\NThose are the leftovers, so I hope that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we don't have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}D-Delicious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Th-The egg rice is delicious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't say you don't have anything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Warm\NWarm
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just seasoned with an egg and soy sauce,\Nso how can it be this good?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:01.03,RightSignL2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In a wide-\Nmouthed pot,\Na pack of\Nsoba-tea\Nis inside
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad you got over your cold, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your nasal voice has finally gone away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything you did for me\Nover the holidays!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rei. Can you sleep with Momo tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that! After all, tomorrow's Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know what, the old lady next door\Ngave us a jigsaw puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Bun-chan's Shopping
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a 1,000 pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's solve it tomorrow in the kotatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Warm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Let's stay here together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why, why, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A home like a warm kotatsu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a match coming up\Nthat I just can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I have to go home and study.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Study? Do you have a test?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's a test where I show my opponent\Nand myself how hard I've been trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you have something to tell Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.72,0:21:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Rei says he has a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. So what do you say at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You say, "Do your best."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Rei, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.62,0:22:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First, Mr. Smith goes up against Gotou,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}while my opponent is Shimada 8th-Dan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.18,0:22:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.09,0:22:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the two winners square off...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in the finals!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wind whistles,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}eliciting a shriek from the harp bridge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That time, I couldn't do anything\Nas he beat me up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I couldn't even give him a scratch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I won't be his punching bag\Non the shogi board.{\i0}
